tech_rep_description: Further media components: sup:AlbumaxII(0.5%),sup:humanSerum(4.3%),sup:Hepes(25 mM),sup:NaHCO3(25 mM),sup:hypoxanthine(0.36 mM),antibiotic:gentamicin(100 µg/mL). Cultures were maintained in leukocyte-depleted red blood cells at 2.5% hematocrit. Compound-resistant parasites were developed using either a high-pressure intermittent (high dose intermittent), a step-wise, or a constant method of compound exposure.
